<DOC><DOCNO> ZF32-151-138 </DOCNO><DOCID>10 766 568</DOCID><JOURNAL>Digital Review  May 20 1991 v8 n20 p10(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Cahners-Ziff Publishing Associates LP 1991.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>SSI's OLTP software picks up support for DEC's SNA gateway.andO;(on-line transaction processing) (Systems Strategies Inc.'sEzBridge OLTP software enhanced)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Briggs, George.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   Systems Strategies Inc. (Product enhancement).andO;Product:   DEC DECnet/SNA Gateway (Gateway device) (Computer programs)ezBridge OLTP (Computer network software) (Product enhancement).andO;Topic:     EnhancementsCommunications Software.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>NEW YORK -- systems Strategies Inc. (SSI), a supplier of LU 6.2-basednetworking software for DEC systems, has announced that its Ezbridge OLTPsoftware now operates over DEC's DECnet/Systems Network Architecture (SNA)Gateway.andM;By offering Ezbridge OLTP for the DEC gateway, SSI gives end users a way oflinking applications across DEc systems and IBM mainframes.andM;SSI adds support for DEC's SNA gateway by building support for DEC'simplementation of the LU 6.2 protocol.andP;  Previously, SSI offered only its ownLU 6.2 implementation on multiple platforms.andM;Ezbridge OLTP works with both the SDLC communications protocol and thechannel-attached version of the DEC gateway, said Bob Gold, SSI's director oftechnology.andM;The software provides distributed message queues over LU 6.2 that offer astandard way of sending transactions in real time between systemsmanufactured by different vendors.andM;SSI touted Ezbridge OLTP as providing assurance of end-to-end delivery ofdistributed messages throughout multicomputing environments.andM;Because it has its own application programming interface, the productprovides the benefits of distributed processing without the pitfallsassociated with the complex problems of application coupling, recovery andintegrity, company officials said.andM;Ezbridge OLTP also supports DEC PC networks, as well as systems from StratusComputer and Tandem Computers.andM;The Ezbridge family comprises three product lines.andP;  Besides Ezbridge OLTP,SSI offers Ezbridge Peer-to-Peer and Ezbridge for Ultrix.andM;Ezbridge OLTP is available now, and is priced from $25,000 to $75,000,depending on configuration and systems employed.andM;Systems Strategies Inc., a Nynex company, is located at 225 W. 34th St., NewYork, NY 10001, (212) 279-8400.andO;</TEXT></DOC>